              "title": "About the Course",
              "content": "Students will explore characteristics shared by all Image-Bearers and learn how to guard against good servants becoming bad masters by continuing Charlotte Mason's text written directly to students. Students begin Book II in this course and finish it in Part 5.\n\nThis topic is included in the following course(s): Citizenship: Grade 10 (U.S.), Citizenship: Grade 10 (Canada)"
